  "description": "Makes Minecraft Hanging Signs and Signs 3D",
  "body": "<br>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img \n   src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c619df175dccd5b1aae708cfb6390d31925124b6.png\"\n    alt=\"3D SIGNS\"\n    width=\"600\">\n</p>\n\n<br>\n\n<hr>\n\n<br>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img \n    src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/17aeebc13d1a3219e7e518d7a7f22a49446d7a4a_0.webp\"\n    alt=\"Description\"\n    width=\"300\">\n</p>\n\n<br>\n\n<p align=\"center\">Why not make the signs 3D? Now you can! This pack makes signs appear the way they should — the player now actually holds the sign, both for regular and hanging signs.</p>\n\n<h1></h1>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img \n    src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/2Xe7NwJu/images/666d8636c9930c178f4e0ac141c64bdd01496690.png\"\n    alt=\"3D SIGNS IMAGE\"\n    width=\"400\">\n</p>\n\n<h1></h1>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img \n    src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/2Xe7NwJu/images/eaa95de5650388e41f1b983156d7614efcb0a892.png\n\"\n    alt=\"3D SIGNS IMAGE2\"\n    style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto;\">\n</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img \n    src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a84a822e69f5e42576ea0631129332b714a27a0a_0.webp\"\n    alt=\"LINKS\"\n    width=\"170\">\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/drigo/projects\" target=\"_blank\">\n    <img src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-wixmp-ed30a86b8c4ca887773594c2.wixmp.com%2Ff%2F159648c2-8de7-4641-a129-8d8c2d06bd9c%2Fdee1zh0-f9e45f11-8ff2-4032-8215-72e54c647a9f.png%3Ftoken%3DeyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..fjO_Mm_jiHcc42PG-UJYYuQBR8JPs7bX9NCjPIfOD6g&n=-1\" width=\"70\" alt=\"CurseForge\">\n  </a>\n  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  <a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/member/drigo/\" target=\"_blank\">\n    <img src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Flh7-rt.googleusercontent.com%2Fdocsz%2FAD_4nXdNMHQhEsV5eId8RgQzyG0GNxBl2Gpb7OQ0y300mcCgU03FMk2DHKoVTJtGA7DA0-KZUEbkNDBAB14my7CItBw_pz5hwycDcHVS7IUNMNY4n7ATuEpK1MDdtL3